==Описание==

The [[Image:Sketcher_BSplineDegree.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_BSplineDegree|Sketcher BSplineDegree]] tool shows or hides the [[B-Splines|B-spline]] degree in all sketches.

[[File:Sketcher B-spline example01.png]]
{{Caption|The number 3 (green, without brackets) in the center refers to the [[Sketcher_BSplineIncreaseDegree|degree]] of the B-spline.}}

